Package gui

Class ClubScreen

java.lang.Object
gui.ClubScreen
public class ClubScreen extends Object
ClubScreen class. The screen where the player manages their team and athletes. Allows players to promote players to and from the main roster. Designate position roles to athletes. The inventory can also be accessed from here.
Author:
Stephen Huang and Jasmine Ong
